core.editor  set editors
git commit.template file-path  : when git commit, this file's content will be commit content,
		you can modify upon that
core.pager  "" means no pager, default is less
user.signingkey  set sign key default, so every time commit willsign for you
core.excludesfile   just like .gitignore, but is global, so useful if want to ignore global
help.autocorrect  set to one then git auto modify your wrong type, give you 0.1s to deny doing that
color.ui  output using color, but if pipe, not use that, so default is false, 
			use --color when pipe
color.branch/diff/status .... you can set colors for them
